{"tid":1481322,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈親口答「爆熱戀MOMO」","createTime":"2019-08-17T16:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T12:41:31.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"296211b8fc4fc380f69cfa3cee13027732e25c4b","tid":1481322,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"南韓男星Super Junior金希澈日前被爆祕密熱戀MOMO，且交往已有2年，不過，這項消息，後來遭到雙方否認。他17日出現在節目《認識的哥哥》，不免成為其他幾位主持人調侃的對象，與他合作歌曲《蝴蝶睡姿》的閔庚勳，在MV裡3人恰好是複雜三角戀，閔庚勳難過地表示：「我對你很失望！」兩人的「基」情互動笑翻所有人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4312/d4312541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4312%2Fd4312541.jpg&h=9e554d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈親口表示與MOMO真的沒關係。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<br />\n金希澈2016年曾與閔庚勳合作歌曲《蝴蝶睡姿》，MV女主角正是TWICE Momo義氣力挺，故事大綱講述3人複雜的三角戀，沒想到，金日前被爆出假戲真做、熱戀Momo。他17日出演節目《認識的哥哥》，自嘲：「我不敢見庚勳了。」解釋與女方的熱戀新聞不是真的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4312/d4312539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4312%2Fd4312539.jpg&h=29d13b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼金希澈、閔庚勳、MOMO在歌曲《蝴蝶睡姿》裡是三角關係。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4312/d4312545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4312%2Fd4312545.jpg&h=1a1f4395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對閔庚勳抗議「我對你很失望，你不可以這樣對我」，金希澈輕聲安撫：「我最喜歡的是你。」他接著保證：「我以後如果跟誰交往的話，會第一個告訴你。」兩人的互動令觀眾哭笑不得，這集播岀後，也有網友幽默留言「總覺得緋聞對象就算不是Momo，也可能是JYP藝人」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4312/d4312543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4312%2Fd4312543.jpg&h=dc704a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈承諾如果交女友的話，會先告訴閔庚勳。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）"},{"pid":"82ef78943b54301f86ee95e35fe24122c413736d","tid":1481322,"uid":256952,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"乜9標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aecb420cd99958aba49e4adee8b7b62895dbe13","tid":1481322,"uid":251836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3c53dbfaeeb21b9c502df197c9aeec27d66b9f","tid":1481322,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"希澈老師好暖.."},{"pid":"65a3cb2a83b3a4ca169a2d497dd7860b38e82061","tid":1481322,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"是但啦 佢幾時先去死呀？"},{"pid":"8422a717b2e195966eeaf88f495f4fd5d51e4c75","tid":1481322,"uid":134432,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"其實導狗唔識字 大家唔好怪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a1639a65289669df227684c7f71a1c8ae0be0e","tid":1481322,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:08:01.000Z","msg":"@丸子熊"},{"pid":"f5352c7726d619b201487ccfb8ba54031d99e388","tid":1481322,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"炒車斷腳落地獄啦"},{"pid":"0ca47726da97dcd5953822b8de3981308ad07474","tid":1481322,"uid":190258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"低汁黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d44939b9243db2b601a326e82ff1bbc0de4714","tid":1481322,"uid":235391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:31:10.000Z","msg":"niconiconi"},{"pid":"30480a46dc08c544780964f9d2cc2c1b095d9fde","tid":1481322,"uid":307982,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:18:58.000Z","msg":"momo又要比人迫退團<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befa92c8c01c7d471cf0305aaa06f16c6dc607dc","tid":1481322,"uid":555,"like":0,